  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>2 cup all-purpose flour</li>
    <li>2 tablespoon sugar </li>
    <li>1/2 teaspoon baking powder</li>
    <li>salt according to taste</li>
    <li>2 cup milk</li>
    <li>3 tablespoon melted butter</li>
    <li>yeast powder </li>
  </ul>
  <h2> Instructions </h2>
  <ol> 
    <li> In a bowl, mix flour, sugar, baking powder and salt.</li>
    <li> In another bowl, whisk milk, melted butter and egg.</li>
    <li> Pour the wet ingredients into the dry ingredients and stir until smooth.</li>
    <li> Heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat and lightly grease it.</li>
    <li> Cook until bubbles form on the surface, then flip and cook until golden
  </ol>

  <p> Enjoy your tasty pancakes! </p>
